com.mobius.vdrapi
Interface INode

All Known Subinterfaces:
IDocumentServer
All Known Implementing Classes:
DocumentServer, ListFactoryNode, PageFactoryNode
public interface INode

A class implements INode to indicate it is a node in a list. By being a node in a list, an object has a factory, a type, a visible value, and a key value.
